        <p>Packaged foods for breakfast and lunch, for all seven days of the week, will be available for pick up for students 18 and under and students receiving special education (up to age 26)<strong> through May 29th </strong> <br><br><strong>LOCATIONS</strong></p>

<p>Alto Elementary parking lot<br>
Impact Church parking lot</p>

<p><strong>DAYS</strong></p>

<p>Tuesdays (meals for three days)<br>
Friday (meals for four days)</p>

<p><strong>TIMES</strong> - 11:00am-12:00pm AND 6:00pm-7:00pm</p>

<p>At this time we have enough volunteers to help.  If you are able to volunteer, Flat River Outreach Ministries (616) 897-8260 is looking for volunteers as their normal volunteers are at high risk for contracting COVID-19.</p>

